{"tid":2068581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"百分之五十六受訪者認為「港人有責任推動中國民主發展」","createTime":"2020-06-17T19:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T11:55:10.000Z","uid":297241,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04b2236c5bc7131a7dc1cc4364b0eadd01e77e50","tid":2068581,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:54:47.000Z","msg":"港大民意研究計劃民調顯示，百分之五十六受訪者認為「港人有責任推動中國民主發展」，認為沒責任的有百分之三十一，後者為一九九三年有紀錄以來新高。民研顯示，有百分之三十一受訪者估計，三年後的中國人權狀况將較現時惡劣，比率同為新高。"},{"pid":"3d8792cb1b71ef29709bdd49e3d665bc28124525","tid":2068581,"uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:56:03.000Z","msg":"2018年5月30日"},{"pid":"1521d1269ddae1a4150072b7220d34f632e957f3","tid":2068581,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:56:33.000Z","msg":"關我Q事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c92432fae40a34b42e56f1226aaa47e6e8ef6bc","tid":2068581,"uid":13467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3d8792cb1b71ef29709bdd49e3d665bc28124525","tid":2068581,"uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:56:03.000Z","msg":"2018年5月30日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:01:05.000Z","msg":"原來舊聞<br />\n又想話香港人唔配有民主個d引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a423ae8b977ae0f9a5c0c82db91398ed2722389","tid":2068581,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:02:46.000Z","msg":"舊聞 拉"},{"pid":"ee36bb0e8e1be6bc7c1ccb4293589daae4e68125","tid":2068581,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:12:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母56%支那豬黎?"},{"pid":"d2e12d0e61d041e0e5827b68ec5a7d415f0ae777","tid":2068581,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee36bb0e8e1be6bc7c1ccb4293589daae4e68125","tid":2068581,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:12:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母56%支那豬黎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:15:20.000Z","msg":"見到成堆中國殖民侵略者仲可以話要有責任幫佢爭民主<br />\n屌你老母人地搞革命一係和平一係武力<br />\n甚至自焚都有<br />\n但冇見過連民主都要威脅其他民族幫佢爭埋咁撚無恥<br />\n去問番班支那仔有冇照過鏡自己配唔配有民主法治<br />\n由君主既自我道德約束到平民既互信包容尊重<br />\n支那有邊一樣做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a50d9764dcb9225e691a2432b1e3028fc16e086","tid":2068581,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:43:29.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"9dfc76deb1c04c0a94e9c3316b515287a2a17f70","tid":2068581,"uid":282897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d8792cb1b71ef29709bdd49e3d665bc28124525","tid":2068581,"uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:56:03.000Z","msg":"2018年5月30日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T00:22:48.000Z","msg":"到左2018年仲有咁多人咁天真."},{"pid":"f76e8cd0282850cfd9fe210e5ac7f7142ef87937","tid":2068581,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"我淨係知一定唔可以比中国有民主<br />\n中国一定要鎖国<br />\n唔可以放中国種出去污染世界"},{"pid":"8d0b458daa52fb002d6f2303588842128fcc7261","tid":2068581,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c92432fae40a34b42e56f1226aaa47e6e8ef6bc","tid":2068581,"uid":13467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3d8792cb1b71ef29709bdd49e3d665bc28124525","tid":2068581,"uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:56:03.000Z","msg":"2018年5月30日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T20:01:05.000Z","msg":"原來舊聞<br />\n又想話香港人唔配有民主個d引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"2018同宜家都冇乜分別㗎啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究計劃今日（2日） 公布六四事件周年民調，發現受訪者主流意見繼續認為中國政府當年處理不當，佔66%，比去年微跌一個百分點，僅15%受訪者認為中央處理正確；支持「平反六四」的比率亦近六成，與過去相約。<br />\n<br />\n問及港人是否有責任推動中國經濟發展，認為有責任的受訪者今年大跌14個百分點至45%，認為沒責任的亦大增10個百分點至45%；<span style=\"color: red;\">認為港人有責任推動中國民主發展的受訪者，比去年大跌10個百分點至51%</span>，認為沒責任的亦有增8個百分點至36%。"}]}